                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48995560/">卢生</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">照片极好。这是要和萧涤非先生一起载入学术史的旅行呀。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1110436361">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1110436361" class="vote-count">0</span>
